description: Now the two really get going. AARON lubes up his hands and swimsinto MASON's hole, one hand, then the other. There's nothingMASON loves better than riding hands and arms and he lets us knowwith beautiful groans and gasps for air. Watching these two playtogether is a great treat. You'll see for yourself as AARON coaxes notone, not two, BUT THREE CREAMY LOADS from MASON GARETwhile MASON's hole opens to full blossom under AARON's artfulcommand.
title: Fistpack 16 - Hand It Over, Scene #05
